      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p110_s0004",
      "text": "The LS_ACC Payload format is shown in table 90. ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        321.0,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p110_s0005",
      "text": "a)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        286.97,
        114.91,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p110_s0006",
      "text": " Hard Address:",
      "bbox": [
        114.91,
        286.97,
        191.29,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p110_s0007",
      "text": " A 24-bit L_Port_ID that consists of:",
      "bbox": [
        191.28,
        286.97,
        348.53,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p110_s0008",
      "text": "A) the 8-bit Domain address in the most significant byte;",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        310.97,
        372.95,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p110_s0009",
      "text": "B) the 8-bit Area address in the next most significant byte; and",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        334.96,
        400.68,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p110_s0010",
      "text": "C) the 8-bit AL_PA that an L_Port attempts to acquire in the LIHA sequence during loop initial-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        358.96,
        539.95,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p110_s0011",
      "text": "izition in the least significant byte (see FC-AL-2).",
      "bbox": [
        138.0,
        370.96,
        352.3,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p110_s0012",
      "text": "If an L_Port does not have a hard address, or if a port does not have FC-AL-2 capability, it shall re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        540.02,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p110_s0013",
      "text": "port zeroes in this field.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        198.64,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
