    },
    {
      "span_id": "p110_s0023",
      "text": "A response shall not be sent to an ADISC if an LR or loop initialization occurs before the LS_ACC is",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        540.02,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p110_s0024",
      "text": "sent. An LS_ACC for a ADISC shall be ignored if an LR or loop initialization occurred between the",
      "bbox": [
